videos.headline: Ragland scores 3-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Miami (OH) quarterback Gus Ragland finds the end zone from 3 yards out to put the first points on the board vs. Kent State.

videos.headline: Kent State QB Barrett takes off for 45 yards
videos.description: Woody Barrett looks to pass but takes it himself for a 45-yard scamper vs. Miami (OH).

videos.headline: Bester plunges in 6-yard TD
videos.description: Miami (OH) running back Jaylon Bester finds the end zone from 6 yards out to extend the RedHawks' lead to 28-0 over Kent State.
